Class FirestoreV1.ListDocuments.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.beam.sdk.io.gcp.firestore.FirestoreV1.ListDocuments.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    FirestoreV1.ListDocuments

    public static final class FirestoreV1.ListDocuments.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
    A type safe builder for FirestoreV1.ListDocuments allowing configuration and instantiation.

    This class is part of the Firestore Connector DSL, it has a type safe builder accessible via FirestoreIO.v1().read().listDocuments().

    See Also:
    FirestoreIO.v1(), FirestoreV1.read(), FirestoreV1.Read.listDocuments(), FirestoreV1.ListDocuments, ListDocumentsRequest, ListDocumentsResponse, google.firestore.v1.Firestore.ListDocuments, google.firestore.v1.ListDocumentsRequest, google.firestore.v1.ListDocumentsResponse
